ENTRY       EC 4.2.3.31                 Enzyme
NAME        ent-pimara-9(11),15-diene synthase;
            PMD synthase
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-oxygen lyases;
            Acting on phosphates
SYSNAME     ent-copalyl-diphosphate diphosphate-lyase [ent-pimara-9(11),15-diene-forming]
REACTION    ent-copalyl diphosphate = ent-pimara-9(11),15-diene + diphosphate [RN:R09681]
ALL_REAC    R09681
SUBSTRATE   ent-copalyl diphosphate [CPD:C06089]
PRODUCT     ent-pimara-9(11),15-diene [CPD:C19810];
            diphosphate [CPD:C00013]
COMMENT     This enzyme is involved in the biosynthesis of the diterpenoid viguiepinol and requires Mg2+, Co2+, Zn2+ or Ni2+ for activity.
HISTORY     EC 4.2.3.31 created 2008
REFERENCE   1  [PMID:17148547]
